      <h2 class="text-headline-md font-display text-on-surface text-balance">Why Data-First Programmatic Wins</h2>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">Cookie deprecation isn't a crisis if you already own your data. We build first-party audience strategies that outperform third-party targeting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">account_circle</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-body-lg mb-3">First-Party Audience Building</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">We help you collect, structure, and activate your own customer data — CRM lists, web visitors, app users — as addressable audiences across all platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">filter_list</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-body-lg mb-3">Precision Targeting Layers</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">Stack contextual, behavioural, demographic, and lookalike signals to reach exactly the right person — reducing wasted spend by up to 40%.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">loop</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-body-lg mb-3">Closed-Loop Attribution</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">Connect ad exposure to actual business outcomes. We track from first impression through purchase — with multi-touch attribution models, not last-click guessing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-action-yellow/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-action-yellow/15 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-action-yellow text-2xl">auto_awesome</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-body-lg mb-3">Creative Automation</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">Dynamic Creative Optimisation (DCO) serves personalised ad variants to each segment in real time — 10x the creative combinations, zero manual effort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-action-yellow/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-action-yellow/15 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-action-yellow text-2xl">location_on</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-on-surface text-body-lg mb-3">Programmatic DOOH</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-sm">Buy digital out-of-home screens programmatically — across 150K screens in Vietnam, Singapore, Indonesia, and across SEA. Target by location, time, audience, and context.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-7 hover:border-action-yellow/40 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-action-yellow/15 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
